# Cancer Detection System

# Overview

This project uses machine learning and deep learning techniques to detect cancer from medical images such as histopathology and X-ray scans.

# Features

* Image classification for cancer detection
* Deep learning models
* Multiple datasets (histopathology, X-ray)
* Model training and evaluation

# Technologies

* Python
* TensorFlow / PyTorch
* OpenCV
* NumPy, Pandas

# Project Structure

* app/ → Application code
* models/ → Trained models
* notebooks/ → Experiments
* scripts/ → Training scripts

# Setup

pip install -r requirements

# Note

Datasets are not included due to size. Download separately.
